texts.content: {"text":"4. Yoki nasihat olar va mav'iza \nunga manfaat berar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,52]}]}

{"text":"7. U poklanmasa, seni hech kim malomat qilmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,46]}]}

{"text":"9. Va U zotdan qo`rqqan holda bo`lgandan esa...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"17. Insonga la'nat bo`lsin, \nuning kofirligi qandoq shiddatli bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"19. Nutfadan uni yaratdi va uni o`lchovli qildi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"23. Yo`q, undoq emas! \nU o`ziga U zot qilgan amrni bajarmadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"32. Sizlarga va chorvalaringizga manfaat va lazzat bo`lsin, deb.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"37. U kunda ulardan har bir shaxsni ovora qiluvchi o`z ishi bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"40. U kunda bir chehralar borki, \nularni g`ubor bosgan.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,55]}]}
